How to use:
    1. Installation: rails plugin install git@github.com:barek2k2/localize-multi-digit.git
    2. Pre-requisite: i18n gem
    3. Usages
        Example:
         - "123".to_ld
         - "abc89efg".to_ld
         - User.first.created_at.to_ld
         - 89.567.to_ld
         - Time.now.to_ld
         - Date.today.to_ld